<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 18:09:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>哈马斯扣押的人质家属并不庆祝贝鲁特暗杀事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-03/ty-article/.highlight/families-of-hostages-held-by-hamas-arent-celebrating-the-beirut-assassination/0000018c-d057-daf6-a5df-d77f46660000</link><description>对于人质家属来说，哈马斯高级人物萨利赫·阿鲁里被杀绝非一张胜利的照片。虽然他们可能不会为他的去世而悲伤，但他们正在哀悼他被暗杀熄灭的希望之火</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 17:35:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-03/ty-article/.highlight/families-of-hostages-held-by-hamas-arent-celebrating-the-beirut-assassination/0000018c-d057-daf6-a5df-d77f46660000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家安全部长本-格维尔宣布将警察局长任期延长六个月</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/natl-security-minister-ben-gvir-announces-hell-extend-police-chiefs-term-by-six-months/0000018c-d054-daf6-a5df-d77c2c8f0000</link><description>这一消息是在科比·沙卜泰 (Kobi Shabtai) 警察局长任期预计结束前几周宣布的。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 17:22:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/natl-security-minister-ben-gvir-announces-hell-extend-police-chiefs-term-by-six-months/0000018c-d054-daf6-a5df-d77c2c8f0000</guid></item><item><title>军方透露，以色列人质萨哈尔·巴鲁克在以色列国防军加沙救援行动中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/israeli-army-says-sahar-baruch-a-hostage-in-gaza-was-killed-during-rescue-operation/0000018c-d034-ddba-abad-d2b57e4d0000</link><description>这名 25 岁的以色列人于 10 月 7 日被绑架，上个月被宣布死亡。周三，军方表示他在一次营救行动中死亡，但许多细节仍不清楚</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 17:14:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/israeli-army-says-sahar-baruch-a-hostage-in-gaza-was-killed-during-rescue-operation/0000018c-d034-ddba-abad-d2b57e4d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡司法政变第二次打击：以色列最高法院推迟实施关键法律</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/second-blow-to-netanyahus-judicial-coup-top-court-delays-implementation-of-key-law/0000018c-d005-d4e1-ad8f-fcb511d20000</link><description>以色列议会三月份通过的所谓“丧失行为能力法”旨在阻止以色列总检察长宣布本杰明·内塔尼亚胡不适合担任公职，即使他违反了他签署的禁止他参与司法系统变革的利益冲突协议。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 16:33:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/second-blow-to-netanyahus-judicial-coup-top-court-delays-implementation-of-key-law/0000018c-d005-d4e1-ad8f-fcb511d20000</guid></item><item><title>自战争开始以来，有 1,600 名以色列士兵患有创伤后应激障碍 (PTSD)； 90人退役</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/1-600-israeli-soldiers-suffer-from-ptsd-since-start-of-war-90-discharged-from-service/0000018c-cfb7-d4e1-ad8f-ffb7ac230002</link><description>据以色列国防军称，大多数创伤后应激障碍病例都是经历过 10 月 7 日哈马斯大屠杀的士兵。以色列国防军心理健康部门担心预备役军人重返平民生活，表示担心“运作困难，日常生活开始变得毫无意义”</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 16:19:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/1-600-israeli-soldiers-suffer-from-ptsd-since-start-of-war-90-discharged-from-service/0000018c-cfb7-d4e1-ad8f-ffb7ac230002</guid></item><item><title>法国和德国谴责以色列部长将大批巴勒斯坦人迁出加沙的呼吁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/eu-countries-condemn-israeli-ministers-calls-to-move-masses-of-palestinians-out-of-gaza/0000018c-cfb7-d4e1-ad8f-ffb7c0100000</link><description>法国和德国对以色列部长斯莫特里奇和本-格维尔的言论进行谴责，美国国务院也罕见地自发谴责</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 15:33:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/eu-countries-condemn-israeli-ministers-calls-to-move-masses-of-palestinians-out-of-gaza/0000018c-cfb7-d4e1-ad8f-ffb7c0100000</guid></item><item><title>欧盟高级外交官博雷尔表示，世界必须强制解决以色列-加沙冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/top-eu-diplomat-borrell-says-world-must-impose-solution-to-israel-gaza-conflict/0000018c-cfc3-d266-a9bf-efc3eb5c0000</link><description>欧盟外交政策负责人何塞普·博雷尔强调了快速解决以色列和哈马斯之间冲突的重要性，并警告说“如果这场悲剧不尽快结束，整个中东可能会陷入战火”</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 15:04:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/top-eu-diplomat-borrell-says-world-must-impose-solution-to-israel-gaza-conflict/0000018c-cfc3-d266-a9bf-efc3eb5c0000</guid></item><item><title>最高法院裁决后，内塔尼亚胡的政党意识到司法改革已死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/following-top-courts-ruling-netanyahus-party-realizes-judicial-reform-is-dead/0000018c-cf6f-d4e1-ad8f-ffffa2da0000</link><description>利库德集团一致认为，无论是短期还是长期，推进司法改革都不再可能。该联盟将失败归咎于总理、司法部长亚里夫·莱文和议员西姆查·罗斯曼</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 14:56:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/following-top-courts-ruling-netanyahus-party-realizes-judicial-reform-is-dead/0000018c-cf6f-d4e1-ad8f-ffffa2da0000</guid></item><item><title>鲨鱼坦克：以加沙为试验场，以色列国防初创企业蓬勃发展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/suicide-drones-and-ai-with-gaza-as-testing-ground-israeli-defense-startups-flourish/0000018c-cf39-ddba-abad-cfb9a3ee0000</link><description>自杀式无人机和人工智能系统：严格的监管和主要国防公司的主导地位意味着以色列每年很少有小型国防初创公司成立。他们正在地缘政治紧张局势、军事预算增加和加沙战争中寻找新机遇</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 13:58:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/suicide-drones-and-ai-with-gaza-as-testing-ground-israeli-defense-startups-flourish/0000018c-cf39-ddba-abad-cfb9a3ee0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么黎巴嫩无法承受真主党和以色列之间的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/why-lebanon-cant-afford-a-war-between-hezbollah-and-israel/0000018c-cf7f-d4e1-ad8f-ffffa45f0000</link><description>黎巴嫩的经济因腐败和无能而受到重创，但最终趋于稳定，游客甚至开始回归。一场全面的战争将对黎巴嫩造成致命打击</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 13:37:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/why-lebanon-cant-afford-a-war-between-hezbollah-and-israel/0000018c-cf7f-d4e1-ad8f-ffffa45f0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯杀害歌手后，这首歌在以色列大受欢迎</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-song-became-a-big-hit-in-israel-after-hamas-killed-its-vocalist/0000018c-cf14-ddba-abad-cfb5db960000</link><description>“很遗憾我没有在她还活着的时候发行这首歌”：10 月 7 日，Ben Ronen 和 Tamar Samet 在 Nova 音乐节上，女歌手被哈马斯恐怖分子杀害后，这首精致而忧郁的歌曲获得了认可</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 13:18:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-song-became-a-big-hit-in-israel-after-hamas-killed-its-vocalist/0000018c-cf14-ddba-abad-cfb5db960000</guid></item><item><title>所有人的目光都集中在纳斯鲁拉身上，真主党领袖准备解决以色列杀害哈马斯官员的问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/all-eyes-on-nasrallah-as-hezbollah-chief-set-to-address-israel-attributed-killing/0000018c-cf20-d4e1-ad8f-ffb18dae0000</link><description>真主党周二表示，阿鲁里在贝鲁特被杀——普遍认为是以色列所为——不会不予答复。然而，一些人认为报复不会立即发生</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 12:34:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/all-eyes-on-nasrallah-as-hezbollah-chief-set-to-address-israel-attributed-killing/0000018c-cf20-d4e1-ad8f-ffb18dae0000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列也是我们的国家”：阿拉伯少数民族在加沙作战，同时面临国内不平等</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-is-our-country-too-the-arab-minority-serving-in-gaza-while-facing-inequality/0000018c-cb4c-d6c4-ab8d-ebfc204b0000</link><description>本周，自战争开始以来，第七名德鲁兹以色列国防军士兵在加沙被杀。在以色列最大的德鲁兹城镇达利亚特卡梅尔，当地人认同以色列，同时谴责其歧视性法律</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 11:44:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-is-our-country-too-the-arab-minority-serving-in-gaza-while-facing-inequality/0000018c-cb4c-d6c4-ab8d-ebfc204b0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯领导人被杀并不影响以色列在加沙的战争——但肯定会影响第二天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/al-arouri-killing-does-not-affect-the-war-in-gaza-but-certainly-the-day-after/0000018c-ce82-ddba-abad-cea30c3d0000</link><description>虽然在贝鲁特杀害哈马斯高级领导人是一次行动上的成功，但它对以色列加沙战争的影响却微乎其微。然而，它有可能加速哈马斯和法塔赫之间的和解，维护哈马斯的地位，并且更重要的是，保证其领导人的生存</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 11:38:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/al-arouri-killing-does-not-affect-the-war-in-gaza-but-certainly-the-day-after/0000018c-ce82-ddba-abad-cea30c3d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议员表示，每个人都清楚加沙人必须被摧毁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/its-clear-to-everyone-gazans-must-be-destroyed-israeli-lawmaker-says/0000018c-ce57-ddba-abad-cef736e40000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡党议员表示，“摧毁”加沙地带公民的广泛呼声证明右翼“一直”都是正确的</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 09:12:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/its-clear-to-everyone-gazans-must-be-destroyed-israeli-lawmaker-says/0000018c-ce57-ddba-abad-cef736e40000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯将在杀害其高级官员后对以色列进行反击。真主党也会报复吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/will-the-killing-of-hamas-leader-in-lebanon-lead-to-further-escalation-with-hezbollah/0000018c-cc0f-dc35-adee-cc4f27010000</link><description>尽管真主党的纳斯鲁拉过去曾威胁要对以色列在黎巴嫩的行动进行报复，但他的行动升级也会限制他的回旋余地</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 04:19:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/will-the-killing-of-hamas-leader-in-lebanon-lead-to-further-escalation-with-hezbollah/0000018c-cc0f-dc35-adee-cc4f27010000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗：苏莱马尼坟墓附近的“恐怖袭击”造成至少103人死亡；真主党纳斯鲁拉谈贝鲁特罢工</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-live/hezbollah-threatens-israel-after-top-hamas-official-al-arouri-killed-in-beirut/0000018c-ccf4-d266-a9bf-edf645660000</link><description>伊朗官方媒体报道称，在被杀将军逝世一周年之际，他的坟墓附近发生了两起爆炸，造成 100 多人死亡。自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,300 名平民和士兵被杀；至少 133 名人质在加沙被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙有 22,313 人死亡、57,296 人受伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 03:53:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-live/hezbollah-threatens-israel-after-top-hamas-official-al-arouri-killed-in-beirut/0000018c-ccf4-d266-a9bf-edf645660000</guid></item><item><title>实际上，为什么不将定居者转移出以色列呢？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/actually-why-not-transfer-settlers-out-of-israel/0000018c-cbc4-dc35-adee-cbc6884a0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 01:22:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/actually-why-not-transfer-settlers-out-of-israel/0000018c-cbc4-dc35-adee-cbc6884a0000</guid></item><item><title>阿巴斯希望美国给予他在加沙的地位并让以色列加入。但可以吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/abbas-expects-the-u-s-to-give-him-authority-in-gaza-but-can-it/0000018c-cbbf-ddba-abad-cbbf79fe0000</link><description>虽然以色列避免讨论战后第二天，但埃及已准备好与巴勒斯坦权力机构合作，并希望能够帮助防止加沙人大规模移民</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 21:24:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/abbas-expects-the-u-s-to-give-him-authority-in-gaza-but-can-it/0000018c-cbbf-ddba-abad-cbbf79fe0000</guid></item><item><title>美国呼吁极右翼以色列部长主张将巴勒斯坦人撤出加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/u-s-calls-out-israeli-ministers-for-advocating-transfer-of-palestinians-out-of-gaza/0000018c-cbec-d4e1-ad8f-fffd3ad60000</link><description>这份声明是美国罕见地不及时批评以色列，更罕见的是它明确点名点名斯莫特里奇和本格维尔。反过来，他们都拒绝了美国的声明，再次强调他们所谓的“自愿移民”的必要性</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 21:16:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/u-s-calls-out-israeli-ministers-for-advocating-transfer-of-palestinians-out-of-gaza/0000018c-cbec-d4e1-ad8f-fffd3ad60000</guid></item></channel></rss>